data.description: Motivated Seller ~ Need more room in the backyard, this home is approx. .25 acre.  Move In Ready for its new owners, can close fast....Check it out...Great Location with easy access to I-10, all the activities of downtown Milton and Blackwater River, so bring the boat for some Summertime fun. Open and Airy Floor Plan featuring Split Bedrooms, Wood look LV Flooring in Foyer, Kitchen, Dining Area and Laundry Room.  Also, a nice Front Porch to Decorate for every Season.  This beautiful home has been freshly painted on the interior and ready for its new owner.  The Great Room is very inviting with a Vaulted Ceiling that is Accented nicely with a Plant Ledge for Displaying Your Favorite Decor - The Kitchen is beautiful with Darker Stained Cabinets, Granite Countertops and equipped with Stainless Appliances Stove, Dishwasher, Microwave and Refrigerator.  The Large Breakfast Bar is great for enjoying a quick snack or Entertaining Guests - Dining Area is nice and cozy to enjoy those delicious meals or to sit back and enjoy your morning coffee.  The Master Suite has plenty of room, is accented with a Trey Ceiling and offers a Walk-in Closet, Double Vanities and Garden Tub for enjoying those most sought after Bubble Baths or if in a hurry, you have the Separate Shower - Other 2 Bedrooms are nice size and they share a Hall Bath - Laundry Room is inside and yes, the washer and dryer stays, this home is ready to move into.  Windows are accented nicely with 2" Blinds, Ceiling Fans in Great Room and Master Bedroom.  Garage has pull down stairs to the attic and Automatic Garage Door Opener.   The nice sized Backyard has an Open Patio and some privacy fencing along the back only, so wouldn't take much to completely fence the rest of the backyard - Check this one out today!!
